<article id="post-363" class="post-363 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-commentary tag-film tag-media tag-stereotypes tag-usa tag-yellowface">
	
	<div class="post-thumbnail">
	<img width="1038" height="576" src="https://jonoyuan.github.io/yellowperilarchive/wp-content/uploads/maxresdefault1-1038x576.jpg" class="attachment-twentyfourteen-full-width size-twentyfourteen-full-width wp-post-image" alt="" />	</div>

	
	<header class="entry-header">
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="cat-links"><a href="https://jonoyuan.github.io/yellowperilarchive/category/commentary/" rel="category tag">Commentary</a></span>
		</div>
		<h1 class="entry-title">East Asians React to Yellowface (via BuzzFeed)</h1>
		<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="entry-date"><a href="https://jonoyuan.github.io/yellowperilarchive/commentary/east-asians-react-to-yellowface-via-buzzfeed/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2015-08-17T14:39:43+00:00">August 17, 2015</time></a></span> <span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://jonoyuan.github.io/yellowperilarchive/author/mp233/" rel="author">Mark Tseng Putterman</a></span></span>			<span class="comments-link"><a href="https://jonoyuan.github.io/yellowperilarchive/commentary/east-asians-react-to-yellowface-via-buzzfeed/#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>
					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p>This BuzzFeed short video shows how East Asian Americans react to Asian caricatures portrayed by white actors in major films from <em>Breakfast at Tiffany&#8217;s</em> (1961) to <em>Cloud Atlas</em> (2012).</p>
<p>Says one viewer:</p>
<blockquote><p>&#8220;You get to a point where you&#8217;re just like: &#8216;I don&#8217;t expect anything better from my media than what I&#8217;ve been given.&#8217; &#8220;</p></blockquote>
<p>Check out the video and leave your comments below.</p>
<p><iframe width="474" height="267" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tarzAjCwAGs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
	<footer class="entry-meta"><span class="tag-links"><a href="https://jonoyuan.github.io/yellowperilarchive/topic/film/" rel="tag">film</a><a href="https://jonoyuan.github.io/yellowperilarchive/topic/media/" rel="tag">media</a><a href="https://jonoyuan.github.io/yellowperilarchive/topic/stereotypes/" rel="tag">Stereotypes</a><a href="https://jonoyuan.github.io/yellowperilarchive/topic/usa/" rel="tag">USA</a><a href="https://jonoyuan.github.io/yellowperilarchive/topic/yellowface/" rel="tag">Yellowface</a></span></footer></article><!-- #post-## -->
